data.description: Welcome to your new haven perfectly situated on a generous corner lot! This delightful home boasts the best eastern exposure, ensuring breezy afternoons perfect for unwinding on your front porch. Accommodate two vehicles easily on the extended driveway, with room for an additional vehicle in the single-car garage. Inside, discover tile throughout the entire home. The large updated kitchen is perfect for any chef, offering tons of counterspace and storage. With updated showers and large walk-in closets in both bedrooms, this home offers plenty of storage with a total of five spacious closets throughout! With a BRAND NEW A/C system. This active community offers a low HOA fee & has a new fitness center, yoga, billiards, shows, gift shop and much more. Only minutes to beaches & restaurants!
